VALUES
  ('elementary-7fec267e-moex-00484', 'elementary-7fec267e', 'elementary-7fec267e-moex-112-34c7f7f6', 'sub-elementary-7fec267e-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '「知識分子既不是調解者，也不是建立共識的人，而是全身投注於批評意識，不願接受簡單 的處方、現成的陳腔濫調，或平和寬容的肯定權勢者的說法或作法。他總是時時維持著警覺 狀態，永遠不讓似是而非的事物或約定俗成的觀念牽著鼻子走。」 根據上文，下列選項何者符合知識分子的特質？', '["不落俗套", "左右逢源", "通才碩學", "韜光養晦 慎思明辨"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "956a0c9fbe15", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1a6f54ad7459", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "501", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 44, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-7fec267e-moex-00485', 'elementary-7fec267e', 'elementary-7fec267e-moex-112-34c7f7f6', 'sub-elementary-7fec267e-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '「心理學的研究上有個現象叫做『破窗效應』，就是說，一個房子如果窗戶破了，沒有人去 修補，隔不久，其它的窗戶也會莫名其妙的被人打破；一面牆，如果出現一些塗鴉沒有清洗 掉，很快地，牆上就布滿了亂七八糟，不堪入目的東西。一個很乾淨的地方，人會不好意思 丟垃圾，但是一旦地上有垃圾出現之後，人就會毫不猶疑地拋，絲毫不覺羞愧。這真是很奇 怪的現象。」 根據上文，下列選項何者符合「破窗效應」的觀點？', '["管理時必須有統一的要求與準則", "防微杜漸是預防問題的手段之一", "人們很容易仿效他人不良的行為", "組織中引進競爭者可以激發活力 環境對人的行為具有強烈誘導性"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "956a0c9fbe15", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1a6f54ad7459", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "501", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 45, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-7fec267e-moex-00486', 'elementary-7fec267e', 'elementary-7fec267e-moex-112-55d283b0', 'sub-elementary-7fec267e-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於法律與道德之比較，下列敘述何者正確？', '["法律與道德的成立與修改皆須經由一定程序才完成", "法律與道德的強制力基礎皆是以國家公權力為後盾", "法律與道德皆為個人行為的規範與評價標準", "法律與道德在我國法體系中皆屬成文法規範"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9565b8c6d34e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "411503a886ab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "501", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "法學大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-7fec267e-moex-00487', 'elementary-7fec267e', 'elementary-7fec267e-moex-112-55d283b0', 'sub-elementary-7fec267e-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依民國108年1月4日修正後的法院組織法，關於最高法院判例的適用，下列敘述何者正確？', '["無裁判全文可資查考之最高法院判例，停止適用", "無裁判全文可資查考之最高法院判例，其效力與未經選編為判例之最高法院裁判相同", "最高法院判例，無論有無裁判全文可資查考，均停止適用", "有裁判全文可資查考之最高法院判例，其效力位階高於未經選編為判例之最高法院裁判"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9565b8c6d34e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "411503a886ab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "501", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "法學大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-7fec267e-moex-00488', 'elementary-7fec267e', 'elementary-7fec267e-moex-112-55d283b0', 'sub-elementary-7fec267e-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '若具體事實不明或難以證明時，法律得為何種立法技術以暫時認定事實？', '["準用", "類推", "推定", "但書"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9565b8c6d34e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "411503a886ab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "501", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "法學大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-7fec267e-moex-00489', 'elementary-7fec267e', 'elementary-7fec267e-moex-112-55d283b0', 'sub-elementary-7fec267e-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '行政機關可在數個合法、可行的途徑中選擇其認為最適合、最可以達成行政目的之方法，此種原則 為：', '["行政一體", "裁量", "事實之涵攝", "一事不再理"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9565b8c6d34e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "411503a886ab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "501", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "法學大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-7fec267e-moex-00490', 'elementary-7fec267e', 'elementary-7fec267e-moex-112-55d283b0', 'sub-elementary-7fec267e-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於自律規則，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["自律規則係地方立法機關基於議會自律權而來，性質上為議會的內部事項規範", "與地方居民之權利義務相關之事項，亦得以自律規則定之", "自律規則除法律或自治條例另有規定外，原則上係由各該立法機關發布，並且須報各該上級政府 備查", "自律規則不得牴觸上級自治法規"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9565b8c6d34e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "411503a886ab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "501", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "法學大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-7fec267e-moex-00491', 'elementary-7fec267e', 'elementary-7fec267e-moex-112-55d283b0', 'sub-elementary-7fec267e-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '修正法規時，如欲廢止或增加少數條文時，應為如何之處理？', '["不保留所廢條文之條次", "保留所廢條文之內容，且須註明「刪除」二字", "得將增加之條文，列在適當條文之後，冠以前條「之一」、「之二」等條次", "增加編或章時，不得冠以「之一」、「之二」等編或章次"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9565b8c6d34e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "411503a886ab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "501", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "法學大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
